{"tid":191512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門公路兩車撞　出九龍全線封閉","createTime":"2017-04-08T03:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T05:15:37.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"981a10b73e899e0728e3036116ba93cf38750b36","tid":191512,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170408/photo/bkn-20170408105432030-0408_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170408110443\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170408%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170408105432030-0408_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170408110443&h=361091dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屯門發生交通意外，早上10時許，一輛中型貨車及客貨車沿屯門公路出九龍，至屯門市廣場附近失控相撞，兩人受傷，救護員到場將傷者送院，警方正在場調查。<br />\n<br />\n受意外影響，屯門公路往九龍方向近屯門市廣場的全線現已封閉，龍尾已到福亨村，運輪署呼籲駕駛人士請考慮改用其他道路。"},{"pid":"66ecf4beb3a76a9c13b8ac81718c876976d0f0f8","tid":191512,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:10:02.000Z","msg":"塞車影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d990569fee127e8a35d065348d43d677c2c171","tid":191512,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:13:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>塞車影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3ccc9ffe542188fd33a713a32d30a4a0890c1b","tid":191512,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfe3630f4e4839b0ff382e32f6f373db4f10f90","tid":191512,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:36:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9338e222e7d790a35b69166f77fe48e828b2ac5b","tid":191512,